From bf894fbe30086d6f1289b37239e391969acf3052 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tobias Weiss <tobias@tobias-weiss.org>
Date: Fri, 17 Jul 2026 09:59:21 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] fix: replace UAParser with regex helpers, add legacy key
 support, fix spoke path

- Replace UAParser.parse/1 (removed dep due to yamerl OTP 23 incompatibility) with Ret.ConnUtils.user_agent_family/1 and user_agent_os/1 regex helpers in media_controller.ex and page_controller.ex

- Add legacy_secret_key_base support to dev.exs and storage.ex for secret key rotation

- Fix spoke page origin path (/spoke suffix) in runtime.exs

- Add deleteClassroomRoom API with bearer auth and Hub.is_creator?/2 ownership check in hub_controller.ex

- Remove ua_parser dependency from mix.exs
